# 🔥 Interview Questions

---

### 1. Difference: List vs Set?

👉 List = duplicates allowed
👉 Set = no duplicates

---

### 2. Difference: HashMap vs HashSet?

👉 HashSet = only values
👉 HashMap = key-value

---

### 3. Why HashMap fast?

👉 Hashing (O(1))

---

### 4. Can HashMap have null?

👉 Yes (1 null key allowed)

